1983;;Hercules;;American;;Luigi Cozzi;;Lou Ferrigno, Sybil Danning;;fantasy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hercules_(1983_film);;The film is a retelling of the story of Hercules (Lou Ferrigno) battling the wizard Minos (William Berger), who uses "science" in an attempt to take over the world. Hercules must stop him and rescue his princess love in the process.